<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Awesome Profile Cards: Paquita Salas</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.1.0/css/all.css"
      integrity="sha384-lKuwvrZot6UHsBSfcMvOkWwlCMgc0TaWr+30HWe3a4ltaBwTZhyTEggF5tJv8tbt"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather|Open+Sans:400,600|Ubuntu"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .viewfinder {
    background: linear-gradient(#bfcdd0, #dde9ed);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
  }
  .viewfinder__card {
    position: relative;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    width: 240px;
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
  }
  .viewfinder__photo {
    height: 200px;
    background-position: center center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
  .viewfinder__card-title {
    display: flex;
  }
  .viewfinder__card-title-titlebox {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .viewfinder__card-title-rectangule {
    height: 42px;
    width: 5px;
    background-color: #438792;
    margin: 20px 15px 0 0;
  }
  .viewfinder__card-title-name {
    padding: 20px 14px 5px 0px;
    font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', 'Comic Sans', 'TSCu_Comic', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 20px;
    color: #114e4e;
  }
  .viewfinder__card-title-job {
    padding: 0 14px 5px 0px;
    font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', 'Comic Sans', 'TSCu_Comic', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 20px;
    color: #54585a;
    font-weight: normal;
  }
  .viewfinder__icons {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    height: 52px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(67, 135, 146, 0.2);
  }
  .viewfinder__icons-box {
    margin-left: 10px;
    border-radius: 22px;
    border: 2px solid #a2deaf;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    color: #114e4e;
  }
  .viewfinder__icons-link {
    color: inherit;
  }
  .palette1 .viewfinder__card-title-rectangule {
    background-color: #438792;
  }
  .palette1 .viewfinder__card-title-name {
    color: #114e4e;
  }
  .palette1 .viewfinder__icons {
    border-bottom-color: rgba(67, 135, 146, 0.2);
  }
  .palette1 .viewfinder__icons-box {
    border: 2px solid #a2deaf;
    color: #114e4e;
  }
  .palette2 .viewfinder__card-title-rectangule {
    background-color: #bd1010;
  }
  .palette2 .viewfinder__card-title-name {
    color: #420101;
  }
  .palette2 .viewfinder__icons {
    border-bottom-color: rgba(189, 16, 16, 0.2);
  }
  .palette2 .viewfinder__icons-box {
    border: 2px solid #e95626;
    color: #420101;
  }
  .palette3 .viewfinder__card-title-rectangule {
    background-color: #eab052;
  }
  .palette3 .viewfinder__card-title-name {
    color: #3e5b65;
  }
  .palette3 .viewfinder__icons {
    border-bottom-color: rgba(223, 229, 235, 0.2);
  }
  .palette3 .viewfinder__icons-box {
    border: 2px solid #a0c0cf;
    color: #3e5b65;
  }
  .typography1 .viewfinder__card-title-name {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  }
  .typography1 .viewfinder__card-title-job {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  }
</style>

  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="viewfinder palette3 typography1">
        <div class="viewfinder__card">
          <div class="viewfinder__card-title">
            <div class="viewfinder__card-title-rectangule"></div>
            <div class="viewfinder__card-titlebox">
              <h2 class="viewfinder__card-title-name">Paquita Salas</h2>
              <h3 class="viewfinder__card-title-job">Programadora FullStack</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="viewfinder__photo"
            title="Foto de la tarjeta"
            style="background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,)"
          ></div>
          <div class="viewfinder__icons">
            <div class="viewfinder__icons-box">
              <a class="viewfinder__icons-link" href="tel:987654321">
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="viewfinder__icons-box">
              <a class="viewfinder__icons-link" href="mailto:paquita.salas@adalab.es">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="viewfinder__icons-box">
              <a
                class="viewfinder__icons-link"
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maricarmen"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="viewfinder__icons-box">
              <a
                class="viewfinder__icons-link"
                href="https://github.com/maricarmen"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <i class="fab fa-github-alt"></i>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
